00:58:37,540 --> 00:58:38,600
 A ne,

1281
00:58:38,600 --> 00:58:39,120
 mi smo ovi,

1282
00:58:39,120 --> 00:58:41,220
 mi smo ovi pravi,

1283
00:58:41,220 --> 00:58:42,680
 mi smo sjedili dok je on prolazi.

1284
00:58:42,680 --> 00:58:45,040
 Mi smo bili kao farizeji.

1285
00:58:45,040 --> 00:58:46,620
 Pa i farizeji su evanđelju,

1286
00:58:46,620 --> 00:58:46,740
 jel?

1287
00:58:46,740 --> 00:58:48,800
 I to je nešto.

1288
00:58:48,800 --> 00:58:51,680
 To je slamka spasa.

1289
00:58:51,680 --> 00:58:52,460
 Znaš,

1290
00:58:52,600 --> 00:58:53,420
 naslijeduj evanđelja,

1291
00:58:53,420 --> 00:58:54,340
 ne moraš baš farizeje.

1292
00:58:54,340 --> 00:58:56,240
 Iako ima jedan,

1293
00:58:56,240 --> 00:58:57,640
 ima by the way,

1294
00:58:57,640 --> 00:58:58,360
 jedan farizeji

1295
00:58:58,360 --> 00:58:59,660
 kojeg bi trebalo naslijedovat.

1296
00:58:59,660 --> 00:59:01,820
 Ne znam jeste li znali,

1297
00:59:01,820 --> 00:59:04,040
 ali jedini danas u svijetu

1298
00:59:04,040 --> 00:59:06,280
 farizejski tekstovi postoje,

1299
00:59:06,280 --> 00:59:08,100
 jedini koji su sačuvani

1300
00:59:08,100 --> 00:59:09,000
 farizejski tekstovi,

1301
00:59:09,000 --> 00:59:09,740
 znate koji su

1302
00:59:09,740 --> 00:59:13,100
 poslanice Svjetoga Pavla Apostola.

1303
00:59:13,100 --> 00:59:15,180
 To su jedini pravi,

1304
00:59:15,180 --> 00:59:16,720
 originalni farizejski tekstovi

1305
00:59:16,720 --> 00:59:17,620
 koji danas postoje.

1306
00:59:17,620 --> 00:59:20,320
 I Pavao je farizej,

1307
00:59:20,320 --> 00:59:21,100
 jedan od deset,

1308
00:59:21,100 --> 00:59:22,320
 za kojih znamo imenom i prezimeno,

1309
00:59:22,400 --> 00:59:23,120
 da je bio farizeji.

1310
00:59:23,120 --> 00:59:24,360
 Tako da,

1311
00:59:24,360 --> 00:59:25,640
 nisu svi farizeji

1312
00:59:25,640 --> 00:59:26,260
 tako loši.

1313
00:59:26,260 --> 00:59:27,460
 Ima i onih

1314
00:59:27,460 --> 00:59:29,100
 kojeg bi se moglo

1315
00:59:29,100 --> 00:59:30,180
 i trebalo naslijedovati,

1316
00:59:30,180 --> 00:59:31,020
 bez kojih ne bi ni bili

1317
00:59:31,020 --> 00:59:31,700
 ovdje danas.

1318
00:59:31,700 --> 00:59:33,020
 Baš zato

1319
00:59:33,020 --> 00:59:33,740
 Isus je bio ljut

1320
00:59:33,740 --> 00:59:34,660
 na one druge farizeje,

1321
00:59:34,660 --> 00:59:35,400
 zato što nisu bili dobri

1322
00:59:35,400 --> 00:59:35,840
 ko i ovi.

1323
00:59:36,920 --> 00:59:37,420
 ali evo,

1324
00:59:37,420 --> 00:59:39,200
 buditi onaj pravi farizej.

1325
00:59:39,200 --> 00:59:39,920
 Farizej znači

1326
00:59:39,920 --> 00:59:40,420
 biti onaj

1327
00:59:40,420 --> 00:59:41,640
 odvojen,

1328
00:59:41,640 --> 00:59:42,480
 onaj gorući,

1329
00:59:42,480 --> 00:59:44,040
 onaj poseban,

1330
00:59:44,040 --> 00:59:45,480
 samo ne moji zastraniti

1331
00:59:45,480 --> 00:59:46,700
 ko oni u posebnost

1332
00:59:46,700 --> 00:59:47,500
 materije

1333
00:59:47,500 --> 00:59:48,680
 i formalizma,

1334
00:59:48,680 --> 00:59:50,140
 nego

1335
00:59:50,140 --> 00:59:52,360
 budi ohrabljen duhom.

1336
00:59:52,360 --> 00:59:53,960
 I za kraj,

1337
00:59:53,960 --> 00:59:55,760
 da nekako to lijepo

1338
00:59:55,760 --> 00:59:56,520
 zaključimo,

1339
00:59:57,400 --> 00:59:58,520
 sve ovo što sam govorio,

1340
00:59:58,520 --> 01:00:00,120
 nemojte se zavaravat,

1341
01:00:00,120 --> 01:00:01,760
 to je meni jasno,

1342
01:00:01,760 --> 01:00:02,320
 vjerujem i vama,

1343
01:00:02,320 --> 01:00:03,360
 to je sve jedna borba.

1344
01:00:03,360 --> 01:00:05,180
 Jedna borba.

1345
01:00:05,180 --> 01:00:06,000
 Nije tu sad stvar,

1346
01:00:06,000 --> 01:00:06,420
 ponavljam,

1347
01:00:06,420 --> 01:00:07,380
 ni naučiti tri glagola

1348
01:00:07,380 --> 01:00:08,020
 na pamet,

1349
01:00:08,020 --> 01:00:10,400
 niti ne znam sad

1350
01:00:10,400 --> 01:00:11,360
 nešto naštrebat,

1351
01:00:11,360 --> 01:00:12,000
 niti sad reći

1352
01:00:12,000 --> 01:00:12,620
 ovo ja sam prosto

1353
01:00:12,620 --> 01:00:13,600
 deset poglavlja više

1354
01:00:13,600 --> 01:00:14,080
 danas.

1355
01:00:14,080 --> 01:00:15,380
 Svaki dan.

1356
01:00:15,380 --> 01:00:17,300
 Čitaš malo po malo

1357
01:00:17,300 --> 01:00:18,220
 i upijaš.

1358
01:00:18,220 --> 01:00:19,060
 Kako god.

1359
01:00:19,060 --> 01:00:20,360
 Ali,

1360
01:00:20,360 --> 01:00:22,820
 budući da ćemo to

1361
01:00:22,820 --> 01:00:23,860
 uskoro čitati,

1362
01:00:23,860 --> 01:00:25,320
 samo bih ti još

1363
01:00:25,320 --> 01:00:26,760
 jedan mali podsjetnik

1364
01:00:26,760 --> 01:00:27,820
 iz Biblije pokazati

1365
01:00:27,820 --> 01:00:29,100
 koliko je to

1366
01:00:29,100 --> 01:00:30,380
 važno

1367
01:00:30,380 --> 01:00:31,920
 i još jednu nijansu.

1368
01:00:31,920 --> 01:00:34,720
 Radi se

1369
01:00:34,720 --> 01:00:36,620
 o četvrtom poglavlju

1370
01:00:36,620 --> 01:00:37,680
 Lukinog evanđelja.

1371
01:00:37,680 --> 01:00:39,940
 Kušnje u pustinji.

1372
01:00:39,940 --> 01:00:41,720
 Kaže ovako.

1373
01:00:41,720 --> 01:00:44,380
 Isus se pun duha svetoga

1374
01:00:44,380 --> 01:00:45,400
 vratio s Jordana

1375
01:00:45,400 --> 01:00:46,640
 i duga četrdeset dana

1376
01:00:46,640 --> 01:00:47,540
 vodio pustinjom

1377
01:00:47,540 --> 01:00:48,960
 gdje ga iskušavao

1378
01:00:48,960 --> 01:00:49,440
 džavao.

1379
01:00:49,440 --> 01:00:51,480
 Tih dana nije ništa jeo,

1380
01:00:51,480 --> 01:00:53,000
 te kad oni istekošeo

1381
01:00:53,000 --> 01:00:53,400
 gladnje.

1382
01:00:53,400 --> 01:00:55,060
 A džavao mu reče,

1383
01:00:55,800 --> 01:00:56,920
 ako si sin Božji,

1384
01:00:56,920 --> 01:00:57,940
 reci ovom kamenu

1385
01:00:57,940 --> 01:00:58,960
 da postane kruhom.

1386
01:00:58,960 --> 01:01:00,580
 Isus mu odgovori,

1387
01:01:00,580 --> 01:01:01,680
 pisano je,

1388
01:01:01,680 --> 01:01:02,660
 ne živi čovjek

1389
01:01:02,660 --> 01:01:03,600
 samo o kruhu.

1390
01:01:03,600 --> 01:01:05,360
 I povede ga džavao

1391
01:01:05,360 --> 01:01:06,020
 na visoko,

1392
01:01:06,020 --> 01:01:06,800
 pokaza mu odjednom

1393
01:01:06,800 --> 01:01:08,180
 sva kraljevstva zemlje

1394
01:01:08,180 --> 01:01:08,780
 i reče mu,

1395
01:01:08,780 --> 01:01:10,020
 tebi ću dati

1396
01:01:10,020 --> 01:01:10,880
 svovu vlast

1397
01:01:10,880 --> 01:01:12,640
 i slavu njihovu,

1398
01:01:12,640 --> 01:01:13,620
 jer meni je dana

1399
01:01:13,620 --> 01:01:14,240
 i komu hoću,

1400
01:01:14,240 --> 01:01:14,780
 dajem je.

1401
01:01:14,780 --> 01:01:16,840
 Ako se dakle pokloniš

1402
01:01:16,840 --> 01:01:18,020
 predamnom sve tvoje.

1403
01:01:18,020 --> 01:01:19,820
 Isus mu odgovori,

1404
01:01:19,820 --> 01:01:21,260
 pisano je,

1405
01:01:21,260 --> 01:01:22,320
 klanjaje se

1406
01:01:22,320 --> 01:01:23,460
 gospodinu Bogu svomu

1407
01:01:23,460 --> 01:01:24,560
 i njemu jedinome služi.

1408
01:01:24,560 --> 01:01:26,120
 Povede ga

1409
01:01:26,120 --> 01:01:26,640
 u Jeruzalem

1410
01:01:26,640 --> 01:01:27,660
 i postavi na vrh hrama

1411
01:01:27,660 --> 01:01:28,180
 i reče mu,

1412
01:01:28,180 --> 01:01:29,900
 ako si sin Božji,

1413
01:01:29,900 --> 01:01:30,980
 baci se odavde dolje.

1414
01:01:30,980 --> 01:01:32,260
 Ta pisano je,

1415
01:01:32,260 --> 01:01:33,860
 anđelima će svojim

1416
01:01:33,860 --> 01:01:34,980
 zapoviditi za tebe

1417
01:01:34,980 --> 01:01:35,740
 da te čuvaju

1418
01:01:35,740 --> 01:01:37,400
 i na rukama će te nositi

1419
01:01:37,400 --> 01:01:38,360
 da se gdje nogom

1420
01:01:38,360 --> 01:01:39,540
 ne spotakneš o kamen.

1421
01:01:40,600 --> 01:01:41,540
 Odgovorimo Isus,

1422
01:01:41,540 --> 01:01:42,960
 rečeno je,

1423
01:01:42,960 --> 01:01:44,960
 ne iskušavaj gospodina

1424
01:01:44,960 --> 01:01:45,680
 Boga svojega.

1425
01:01:45,680 --> 01:01:48,160
 I pošto iscrpi sve kušnje,

1426
01:01:48,160 --> 01:01:49,360
 džavao se udalje od njega

1427
01:01:49,360 --> 01:01:50,240
 do druge prilike.

1428
01:01:50,240 --> 01:01:52,920
 Znači, Isus je pobjedio

1429
01:01:52,920 --> 01:01:54,280
 džavla u svakoj kušnji

1430
01:01:54,280 --> 01:01:55,740
 svojom riječju.

1431
01:01:55,740 --> 01:01:57,480
 To je prva stvar.

1432
01:01:57,480 --> 01:01:58,760
 Međutim,

1433
01:01:58,760 --> 01:01:59,840
 nije baš tako jednostavno

1434
01:01:59,840 --> 01:02:00,240
 zašto?

1435
01:02:00,240 --> 01:02:01,640
 Džavao je došlo,

1436
01:02:01,640 --> 01:02:03,380
 prvo je krenuo sa napašću,

1437
01:02:03,380 --> 01:02:04,940
 malo, aha, gladni smo,

1438
01:02:04,940 --> 01:02:06,500
 joj, to su moje potrebe,

1439
01:02:06,500 --> 01:02:07,700
 to je moje tijelo,

1440
01:02:07,700 --> 01:02:08,500
 tema biologija,

1441
01:02:08,500 --> 01:02:09,240
 znači, to je nešto,

1442
01:02:09,240 --> 01:02:09,840
 na kraju kraja,

1443
01:02:09,840 --> 01:02:11,460
 nije grijeh biti gladan,

1444
01:02:11,460 --> 01:02:13,800
 nije grijeh nahraniti se,

1445
01:02:13,800 --> 01:02:15,260
 za bi bio grijeh

1446
01:02:15,260 --> 01:02:16,960
 pretvoriti taj kamen u kruh.

1447
01:02:16,960 --> 01:02:19,060
 Međutim,

1448
01:02:19,060 --> 01:02:20,980
 Isus odgovara Božjom riječju.

1449
01:02:20,980 --> 01:02:22,060
 Pisano je.

1450
01:02:22,060 --> 01:02:23,360
 U drugoj kušnji,

1451
01:02:23,360 --> 01:02:24,200
 pa, džavao njemu kože,

1452
01:02:24,200 --> 01:02:25,980
 ej, ajde se baci dolje,

1453
01:02:25,980 --> 01:02:27,120
 pisano je.

1454
01:02:27,120 --> 01:02:29,960
 Džavao isto zna dobro Bibliju,

1455
01:02:29,960 --> 01:02:30,720
 jako dobro.

1456
01:02:30,720 --> 01:02:32,960
 I on ponavlja,

1457
01:02:32,960 --> 01:02:33,920
 Isus njemu odgovara,

1458
01:02:33,920 --> 01:02:35,340
 opet pisano je,

1459
01:02:35,340 --> 01:02:35,980
 još nešto drugo.

1460
01:02:35,980 --> 01:02:37,300
 Džavao ide opet,

1461
01:02:37,340 --> 01:02:38,640
 a pisano je ovako.

1462
01:02:38,640 --> 01:02:40,680
 A onda Isus odgovara,

1463
01:02:40,680 --> 01:02:42,320
 rečeno je.

1464
01:02:42,320 --> 01:02:44,700
 Kad je nešto pisano,

1465
01:02:44,700 --> 01:02:46,080
 to se pročita.

1466
01:02:46,080 --> 01:02:48,420
 I to će džavao imitirati

1467
01:02:48,420 --> 01:02:49,060
 bez problema.

1468
01:02:49,060 --> 01:02:50,540
 Međutim,

1469
01:02:50,540 --> 01:02:52,200
 kada ti tu riječ

1470
01:02:52,200 --> 01:02:53,120
 ne samo čitaš,

1471
01:02:53,120 --> 01:02:54,380
 nego kad ju čuješ,

1472
01:02:54,380 --> 01:02:56,080
 onda ju moraš i

1473
01:02:56,080 --> 01:02:58,020
 poslušat.

1474
01:02:58,020 --> 01:03:00,200
 E, tu džavao više nije

1475
01:03:00,200 --> 01:03:01,320
 imao šta za reći.

1476
01:03:01,320 --> 01:03:02,520
 Tu više nije rekao,

1477
01:03:02,520 --> 01:03:03,160
 ej, znaš,

1478
01:03:03,160 --> 01:03:05,420
 moglo bi se poslušat,

1479
01:03:05,420 --> 01:03:06,460
 ne, ne, ne, ne.

1480
01:03:06,980 --> 01:03:09,620
 džavao ne može slušat.

1481
01:03:09,620 --> 01:03:11,220
 Dragi moji,

1482
01:03:11,220 --> 01:03:12,660
 to je izvor blagoslova.

1483
01:03:12,660 --> 01:03:13,820
 Blagoslov,

1484
01:03:13,820 --> 01:03:14,860
 lijepa riječ,

1485
01:03:14,860 --> 01:03:16,040
 sama riječ ti govori.

1486
01:03:16,040 --> 01:03:17,740
 Evo, želim svima vama,

1487
01:03:17,740 --> 01:03:18,880
 draga braćo i sestre,

1488
01:03:18,880 --> 01:03:21,120
 da vam ovaj korizmeni hod,

1489
01:03:21,120 --> 01:03:22,540
 koji ćemo za desetak dana

1490
01:03:22,540 --> 01:03:23,620
 započeti,

1491
01:03:23,620 --> 01:03:24,540
 još na Valentinovo,

1492
01:03:24,540 --> 01:03:25,320
 kako predivno,

1493
01:03:25,320 --> 01:03:27,020
 da vam bude to,

1494
01:03:27,020 --> 01:03:27,960
 evo, stvarno vrijeme

1495
01:03:27,960 --> 01:03:29,340
 osluškivanja,

1496
01:03:29,340 --> 01:03:30,900
 produbljivanja,

1497
01:03:30,900 --> 01:03:32,700
 upoznavanja

1498
01:03:32,700 --> 01:03:34,640
 ljubavi Kristove

1499
01:03:34,640 --> 01:03:35,740
 kroz njegovu riječ.

1500
01:03:35,740 --> 01:03:37,240
 I želim,

1501
01:03:37,240 --> 01:03:38,580
 evo, jedva čekam,

1502
01:03:38,580 --> 01:03:40,520
 da svaki od vas doživi

1503
01:03:40,520 --> 01:03:42,600
 neopisiva čudesa,

1504
01:03:42,600 --> 01:03:43,740
 njegovog milosrđa,

1505
01:03:43,740 --> 01:03:44,980
 njegove ljubavi,

1506
01:03:44,980 --> 01:03:47,220
 kada ga budeš gledao u oči

1507
01:03:47,220 --> 01:03:48,100
 i kada čuješ

1508
01:03:48,100 --> 01:03:50,900
 ti si sin moj ljubljeni,

1509
01:03:51,700 --> 01:03:53,520
 u tebi mi svamilina.

1510
01:03:53,520 --> 01:03:56,400
 Slava Otcu i Sinu

1511
01:03:56,400 --> 01:03:57,540
 i Duhu Svetomu.

